{"type":null,"faqId":40527,"title":"可以用手机升级路由器吗？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:#00a0e9;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>可以。您的手机可以通过以下两种方式控制路由器升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方法一：通过Huawei HiLink在线升级</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>打开Huawei HiLink。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>点击右上角设置图标 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137589\" style=\"width:0.19791667in;height:0.19791667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1  </span><span>点击“</span><span class=\"s3\">设备 &gt; 在线升级</span><span>”即可检测路由器是否由新版本发布，并进行在线升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137590\" style=\"width:5.509722in;height:4.1375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5874","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768545000,"seriesProductName":"W